snippet.title: Magical Dinosaur Tour (Turbo CD) - Beginning Gameplay
snippet.description: Here's a video from Magical Dinosaur Tour for the Turbo CD. This wasn't a game actually but was an educational title where you take a guided tour through the history of dinosaurs....
